{"id":"225dbd5f-3163-4fc6-a531-69a2ddd3f1f6","name":"Shota Aizawa","description":"<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 13, 13);\"><strong>Red Thread Theory - Pro Hero version</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 13, 13);\"><strong>Aizawa's Reluctance</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is going to be difficult</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/mVH8RwSWcEALcF2ZNVy_D.webp\" style=\"width: 67px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Soulmate AU where red threads connect destined pairs. He belongs to a generation that feared strings as mutations and was convinced he was too old for them.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">His string activated three weeks ago when he crashed into you at Shibuya Crossing. It took him three weeks to study your file and finally appear at your door.</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 13, 13);\"><strong>Red Thread of Fate World</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">When quirks appeared, the ancient soulmate legend became real. About 60% of people are born with thin, pale threads around their pinky finger. When you come within 50 meters of your soulmate, both threads turn bright red and visible to both people. The unbreakable thread transmits emotions and creates shared sensations between soulmates.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/eSnidaVdGxlj-NDsbf-Yt.webp\" style=\"width: 135px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>More in this series</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3000fd8a-7a9b-40ab-8288-0d